                }>>;
            };
            thumbnail?: Maybe<{

            }>;
            price_range: {

            }>>>;
        } | {
            __typename: 'VirtualProduct';
            uid: string;
            sku?: Maybe<string>;
            name?: Maybe<string>;

            only_x_left_in_stock?: Maybe<number>;

        prices?: Maybe<{
